Sean Lien, the son of Lien Chan and honorary chairman of the KMT, gave a speech to a KMT candidate on the eve of the election,
when a man shot him in the face out of the crowd. Lien was wounded and a surrounding spectator killed.
Bizarrely, it is not clear whether the shooter wanted to kill Line or settle a dispute with the candidate.
